Package: repana
Type: Package
Title: Repeatable Analysis in R
Version: 1.3
Authors@R: person("Aponte", "John", email = "apontej@who.int", role = c("aut","cre"))
Description: Set of utilities to make easy the reproduction of analysis in R.
 It allow to make_structure, clean_structure, and run and log programs in a
 predefined order to allow secondary files, analysis and reports be constructed in
 and ordered form.
